{"tid":1199094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 高鐵石崗車廠3工人觸電2命危","createTime":"2019-06-10T11:42:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T12:11:14.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a0e17fcbffd5ef348ec05df6d494a4425308d31b","tid":1199094,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:42:56.000Z","msg":"高鐵石崗車廠再發生嚴重工業意外，今日(10日)下午3名男技工在列車停放處維修電纜時，懷疑同時意外觸電，導致身體多處受傷，救護員趕至替3名傷者治理及送院，其中1人需以紗布敷面及戴氧氣罩協助呼吸，目前勞工處正調查意外原因。港鐵稱已即時暫停該承辦商的相關工程項目。這是同一車廠十個月內發生的第2宗工業意外。<br />\n<br />\n現場廣深港高鐵（香港段）石崗車廠，今日中午12時許，3名分別姓黃（29歲）、姓顏（35歲）及姓胡（31歲）承辦商維修男工人，於列車停放處內的工程車升降工作台上，正為特定範圍的架空電纜，進行日常維修檢查。據悉，該維修工作於早上約10時許開始。現場消息，3名工人在埋頭工作之際，懷疑同時意外觸電，其他工人見狀隨即上前了解，同時通知高鐵車務控制中心報警。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190610/bkn-20190610181603552-0610_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190610%2Fbkn-20190610181603552-0610_00822_001.html&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3Xtw13VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=9ac1d88a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190610/bkn-20190610181603552-0610_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"528b490e4950c658055421a26a5ba0e6eba25514","tid":1199094,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:44:29.000Z","msg":"correct link<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190610/bkn-20190610131332230-0610_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190610%2Fbkn-20190610131332230-0610_00822_001.html&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3Xtw13VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=cd983354\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190610/bkn-20190610131332230-0610_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"dfb7d692f29466e5369309a86f16eb3431c9cee1","tid":1199094,"uid":225347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:54:25.000Z","msg":"求gif<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"